            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%B3%A8%E5%B0%846%E9%92%88%E7%8E%BB%E5%B0%BF%E9%85%B8%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%B4%E8%87%B4%E6%AE%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%B3%A8%E5%B0%846%E9%92%88%E7%8E%BB%E5%B0%BF%E9%85%B8%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%B4%E8%87%B4%E6%AE%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女子注射6针玻尿酸填充额头致残#</span></a>】90后姑娘小雪，在一酒店内注射玻尿酸填充额头，却因操作不当致中央动脉堵塞，留下终身残疾。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E5%90%88%E8%A7%84%E4%BD%86%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%93%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%B4%E6%AF%81%E5%AE%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E5%90%88%E8%A7%84%E4%BD%86%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%93%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%B4%E6%AF%81%E5%AE%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医美产品合规但操作不当也可致毁容#</span></a> 友友们一定要注意，即使要做医美，也要选择正规医院，不要自行操作！👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4871206747439169" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hb9vhyx14jj60rs0fmgu402.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Dauec7bylx083ij4PWMo01041201JzJ00E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1676947097&amp;ssig=xAKlVuXzHx&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/wf668Ydxlx083ij3nPuM01041200TQRX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;templa