            <description><![CDATA[创可贴，不是“万能贴”！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>如何判断伤口是否适合贴创可贴？记住这3个条件：<br><br>1⃣️伤口小：长度不超过创可贴的宽度。<br>2⃣️较表浅：深度不超过2-3毫米，出血少。<br>3⃣️无需缝合的刀切伤、玻璃划伤、擦伤、针扎伤等。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hb8pp14bgkj20oi0j0mya.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
